===Verb===
'''mixed'''

# Past tense and past participle of [[mix]].

===Adjective===
'''mixed'''  ({{compar}}: '''more mixed''', {{superl}}: '''most mixed''')

# Having two or more separate aspects.
#:''I get a very mixed feeling from this painting.''
# Not completely pure.
#:''My joy was somewhat mixed.''
#''(sporting)'': co-ed
#:''The tennis match was '''mixed''' with a male and a female on each side.''

